      "narrationText": "Esiteks tunnel käsk. Rakendus töötab serveris, mitte sinu sülearvutis. CLI repo tunnel suunab konteineri pordi üle SSH, nii et saad selle brauseris localhost aadressil avada.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-01-after.9d140616.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.474286,
