      "audioDurationSec": 13.400816,
      "textHash": "aab6bbcfd6deb10f891a8c6bb14b31ba759d4839102746ead62730800c8ad6bb",
      "narrationText": "Teiseks term käsk. CLI term connect viib sind repositooriumi liivakasti -- sama isoleeritud vaate, mida VS Code annaks. Käivita suvaline käsk selle repositooriumi Dockeri deemoni vastu ilma terminalist lahkumata.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-02-after.83b74d9b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.362449,
      "afterTextHash": "83b74d9b337e39917159361f463526846b42a06c282add5ddc2ca7f5bf6cb780"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-work-with-repo-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 15.893309,
      "replayEndSec": 22.144638,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-03.bac87e7c.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.247347,
      "textHash": "bac87e7cc11b0179c9e91e5d0345fb35ef5656d980bf01e014df35000349068a",
      "narrationText": "Enne failide tõugramist vaata eelvaadet --dry-run abil. See näitab täpselt, mis muutuks, ilma midagi kopeerimata. Kasuta alati eelvaadet, kui oled ebakindel.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-03-after.6e025361.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.429388,
      "afterTextHash": "6e025361972ec725111b3f2432be40986d347bb3c5dc18a09b88998a8feccab3"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-work-with-repo-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 22.144638,
      "replayEndSec": 30.993341,
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-04.5df2e073.mp3",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.479184,
      "textHash": "5df2e07358117742ea4a2892cc86ac37eb4e4d0c2559571414652bc0307b9ef0",
      "narrationText": "Nüüd teeme päris üleslaadimise. CLI repo sync upload liigutab failid sinu sülearvutist repositooriumisse üle SSH rsync delta tihendusega. Tunnel, term, sync -- kolm käsku katavad igapäevase tsükli.",
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/en/tutorial-work-with-repo/tutorial-work-with-repo-04-after.f227dfa2.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.709388,
      "afterTextHash": "f227dfa2fe0c2e685cd819748cd3633e7d9d973c66d2239bb504b416a464648e"
    }
